      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'This is a bunch of lore, that we have spent thousands of hours creating.
    The number is 4. We will never tell you the number directly, but only show it
    in lore.


    We will be adding more lore, at some point in time. But right
    now, this is all you get.


    Sir Edward Hall Moris II, once married Elaine.
    Sir Morris II was about 50 at the time, but Madam Elaine was much much younger,
    at the young age of only 26. She soon became pRaGnEnT but Sir Edward II did not
    approve. He tied her up in the basement, and left. [More lore on next page]'
